export const lightTheme = {
    body: '#fff',
    // header //
    gappsfill: 'hsl(220deg 5% 39%)',
    gappshover: 'hsl(240deg 3% 92%)',
    gappsafterbackground: 'hsl(220deg 5% 39%)',
    gappsaftercolor: 'hsl(240deg 3% 92%)',
    signinbackground: '#1a73e8',
    signinhoverbackground: '#4285f4',
    signincolor: '#fff',
    signinborder: 'transparent',
    signinhoverborder: '#4285f4',
    // search language //
    searchlanguagecolor: '#3c4043',
    searchlanguageacolor: '#1a0dab',
    // search bar //
    searchbarborder: 'hsl(230deg 10% 89%)',
    searchbarhovershadow: 'rgb(32 33 36 / 28%)',
    searchbarhoverborder: 'rgb(223 225 229 / 0%)',
    searchiconfill: 'hsl(217deg 7% 63%)',
    searchbariconfill: 'hsl(216deg 4% 46%)',
    clearbuttondivider: 'hsl(230deg 9% 87%)',
    searchbartextcolor: 'hsl(0deg 0% 15%)',
    searchbartexthighlight: '',
    // search button //
    searchbuttontextcolor: 'hsl(0deg 0% 25%)',
    searchbuttonbackground: 'hsl(210deg 17% 98%)',
    searchbuttonborder: '',
    searchbuttonhoverborder: 'hsl(230deg 9% 87%)',
    // settings panel //
    panel: '#fff',
    panelborder: '#70757a',
    panelseparator: '#ebebeb',
    themeiconfill: 'hsl(210deg 4% 46%)',
    // footer //
    footerbackground: 'hsl(0deg 0% 95%)',
    footertextcolor: 'hsl(0deg 0% 45%)',
    footercountryborder: 'hsl(230deg 9% 87%)',
  }
